name: DogKing On XLayer
description: DogKing is the ultimate meme revolution on OKX’s XLayer chain, blending the spirit of Doge culture with the power of cutting-edge blockchain tech. Born from the creativity of meme enthusiasts and crypto pioneers, DogKing has quickly grown into a global community movement centered on fun, inclusivity, and financial empowerment. With its bold personality and loyal following, DogKing isn’t just another meme token—it’s the crown jewel of the XLayer meme storm, uniting DOG lovers across chains and setting the stage for a new era of community-driven crypto culture.
